text: Maria Matthaiou (born 26 April 1997) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for First Division club Lefkothea Latsion and the Cyprus women's national team. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers
